com.betfair.cougar.transport.api.protocol.events

Interface EventMarshaller<T>


  • public interface EventMarshaller<T>
    This interface describes a marshaller for the supplied Event transport. The marshaller will turn an object that extends Event into an appropriate form to be emitted by your transport
